data.description: New Construction mobile home on permanent foundation, 2.8 +/- acres, Hart County, Canon GA. Ready in 60 days from binding contract.  3 bedroom, 2 bath or possibly 4/2 if you contract before the order is made. This home comes with a standard 6'x6' deck on the back and 8'x12' on the front. Other deck options are available (larger and/or covered) for an additional cost. A non-refundable deposit required for these changes. Great location on a quiet street between Bowersville and Canon. Just a short drive to Lavonia, Hartwell, or Royston. Will qualify for FHA, VA, Conventional. Some photos are taken from the same mobile home in another location. Finishes, elevation, and interior may vary.
